      <event start="T685-245" end="T267">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T267" end="T109">pač eem ... </event>
      <event start="T109" end="T268">wireless si, </event>
      <event start="T268" end="T110">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T110" end="T695-164">Saj imaš tudi eee pol AirPods Pro and what not. </event>
      <event start="T699-337" end="T700-328">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T702-147" end="T705-08">Mh. </event>
      <event start="T715-97" end="T112">Nekaj cajta nazaj sem drugače tudi gledal za isto ceno, </event>
