      <event start="T1015-494" end="T1018-458">Ampak si rekel, da je Mini-LED best of both worlds. </event>
      <event start="T1020-214" end="T1024-446">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1037-734" end="T147">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T147" end="T1044-801">to je kao v tem iPadu Pro so ta Tandem, k so dva OLED ekrana en na drugega dali, </event>
      <event start="T1044-801" end="T1047-237">so kao dosegli višji brightness. </event>
      <event start="T1049-409" end="T1050-748">Pač tako pravijo. </event>
      <event start="T1052-464" end="T324">Ja glej, </event>
      <event start="T324" end="T149">če imaš dva ... </event>
      <event start="T149" end="T325">it's more than one, </event>
      <event start="T325" end="T1056-201">right? [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T1065-427" end="T327">Oh, </event>
      <event start="T327" end="T1067-282">it's just too ... [nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T1069-751" end="T1070-813">Eh. </event>
      <event start="T1089-233" end="T1091-016">Mh. </event>
      <event start="T1099-664" end="T1102-493">Imam še eno, še eno tako tehnološko. </event>
      <event start="T1102-493" end="T1105-062">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T1105-062" end="T1111-208">Eem Pixel eight ali Pixel nine a? </event>
      <event start="T1113-162" end="T1114-873">Res je. </event>
      <event start="T1114-873" end="T1118-841">Pa recimo, da bi naslednje leto hotel nov telefon kupit. </event>
      <event start="T1121-726" end="T1123-422">Ten d() ten a. </event>
      <event start="T1124-516" end="T199">Ful še nisem šel primerjat, kaj sploh eem zgubiš slash pridobiš s tem, </event>
      <event start="T199" end="T1133-92">če bi šel zdaj konkretno na nine ali nine a. </event>
      <event start="T1136-647" end="T1138-72">Kaj je razlika med devet pa devet a? </event>
      <event start="T1144-696" end="T1146-016">A si ga že videl drugače? </event>
      <event start="T1147-355" end="T1148-873">Tisto na sliki. </event>
      <event start="T1153-046" end="T1155-693">Nima nima več camera bumpa. </event>
