      <event start="T1178-847" end="T1180-88">[nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T1180-88" end="T334">Aja, </event>
      <event start="T334" end="T1181-844">to je z ovitkom vred? </event>
      <event start="T1185-65" end="T1187-902">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1187-902" end="T337">Pač ... [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T337" end="T1191-287">Ooh. </event>
      <event start="T1197-572" end="T1199-823">Ne vem, mogoče po zaenkrat. </event>
      <event start="T1211-268" end="T1213-655">Ja ne vem, če je v embalaži. </event>
      <event start="T1218-623" end="T1225-174">Jaz sem pa videl eem sixteen e, iPhone. </event>
      <event start="T1226-196" end="T1231-162">[smeh] Čis ... [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1231-162" end="T1234-411">Ne vem, tisti se mi pa res ne ne zdi eem vredno. </event>
      <event start="T1234-411" end="T1241-379">Ker dobiš pač kakšne rabljene petnajstke ali pa štirinajstke, ki so pač boljše kakor oni sixteen e. </event>
      <event start="T1250-696" end="T344">Prišparaš na bateriji, </event>
      <event start="T344" end="T1252-234">a ne? </event>
      <event start="T1272-794" end="T1276-174">Pa se mi zdi, da so še na nekih Wi-Fi antenah pa tem prišparali. </event>
      <event start="T1277-355" end="T1278-992">Mhm. </event>
      <event start="T1286-395" end="T1289-756">[smeh] Eem. </event>
      <event start="T1289-756" end="T1292-265">Pa nima wireless charginga. </event>
      <event start="T1294-774" end="T1304-119">So pa rekli, da bodo nars() naredili iPhona, k bo brez katerih koli priključkov. </event>
